Exclusions¶

Target proportion is less than .10¶

  • NQs & FQ (Model A): 6 pilot subjects excluded
  • NQs & FQ (Model B): 8 pilot subjects excluded
  • NQs only (Model A): 10 pilot subjects excluded
  • NQs only (Model B): 9 pilot subjects excluded

Average standard deviation across target and biased guessing distributions (weighted by respective proportion fits) exceeds 70 degrees.¶

targetRQ = targetfit + RQfit + FQfit;

if targetfit < .15 || ((targetfit * targetSD) + (RQfit * biasedSD) + (FQfit * biasedSD) / targetRQ > 70
  • NQs & FQ (Model A): 3 more pilot subjects excluded
  • NQs & FQ (Model B): 1 more pilot subjects excluded
  • NQs only (Model A): 3 more pilot subjects excluded
  • NQs only (Model B): 1 more pilot subjects excluded
